HEADWORD: Corporealist
<hw>Cor*po"re*al*ist</hw>
<pr>(k⟦ocr⟧r*p⟦omac⟧"r⟦esl⟧*⟦ait⟧l*⟦icr⟧st)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One
